{"CLs":[{"__type":"IST","EID":"f509e32a-5ec0-42e6-bed5-09c82b0160ac","H":2623.6,"TXT":"(* \u000d\u000a * Version 1.3.1 :\u000d\u000a * - First major version after Eastwood and Metalworks\u000d\u000a * - Incoporates shear controls, encoder monitoring of main feeder\u000d\u000a * - added a new operations page on the HMI\u000d\u000a * - corrected a few bugs with unit conversion on encoder\u000d\u000a * - not using the calc found in the Feed_Encoder sections - now using a manual Encoder roller size set on the features HMI page\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a(*\u000d\u000a * Version 1.4.0 :\u000d\u000a * - Added straightner encoders\u000d\u000a * - Adding ABB ethercat drive for uncoiler\u000d\u000a *  ^--- Adding ethercat ACS880 variables to IO Map and toggle between sensor speed and preset speed\u000d\u000a * - Fixed a bug with coil cart forward and reverse, they were inverse of what they should be\u000d\u000a * - Added alarms so that the user knows when the coil cart cannot move because of a condition\u000d\u000a * - Changed the logic for the coil keeper so that it is only one selector\u000d\u000a * - Changed the selector logic for the pressing arm\u000d\u000a * - Redid speed control for the uncoiler ethercat drive\u000d\u000a * - Added shaker logic to C_Press, revisted the timer\u000d\u000a * - Added back in the FR3 & FR4 feedback error\u000d\u000a * - Redid the safety program\u000d\u000a * - Added uncoiler signals to ABB_ECAT\u000d\u000a * - Added IO Link sensors for feeder and uncoiler\u000d\u000a * - Added Temperature control for Etalex\u000d\u000a * - Added Off mode\u000d\u000a * - Removed the blue button as a reset button\u000d\u000a * - Made communication via ACS control for uncoiler drive possible\u000d\u000a * - Began working on auto-compensation feeder mode\u000d\u000a * - Auto compensation is working ok, need more modifications\u000d\u000a * - Modifications to the auto compensation mode\u000d\u000a * - Changed the enable switch logic\u000d\u000a * - Added signals for the safety from safety controller\u000d\u000a * - Added a speed limit to the uncoiler enable switch control\u000d\u000a * - Changed the straightner encoder mode for one with a cam \u000d\u000a * - Added Shaker Overload fault to top stop conditions\u000d\u000a * - Changed overrun verification angles\u000d\u000a * - Fixed ACS Ethercat block to output actual variables rather than using externals, added another stop code for high inertia loads\u000d\u000a * - Made sure shaker cannot start in inch mode, also added a bypass for commissioning\u000d\u000a * - Etalex temp control - inverted IO Link byte order\u000d\u000a * - Added IO Link EOM sensor to EOM alarms\u000d\u000a * - Added master axis error to motion faults\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a \u000d\u000a (*\u000d\u000a * - Added servo adjustment motor\u000d\u000a * - Added shear cycles\u000d\u000a * - Added automatic shear cycles\u000d\u000a * - Two sensor option for uncoiler\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a(* Version 1.6.0\u000d\u000a * - Added Abort Feed signal to UIO\u000d\u000a * - Added feed calculations\u000d\u000a * - Added die metrics and counters\u000d\u000a * - Added Auto-compensated top stop\u000d\u000a * - Added precision to the encoder in order to do smaller inch movement without start time becoming an issue\u000d\u000a * - Added speed as SPM for ECAT type drives\u000d\u000a * - Merged all recipes into one\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a(* Version 1.6.0\u000d\u000a * - Added Abort Feed signal to UIO\u000d\u000a * - Added feed calculations\u000d\u000a * - Added die metrics and counters\u000d\u000a * - Added Auto-compensated top stop\u000d\u000a * - Added precision to the encoder in order to do smaller inch movement without start time becoming an issue\u000d\u000a * - Added speed as SPM for ECAT type drives\u000d\u000a * - Merged all recipes into one\u000d\u000a * - Corrections made to the original program - added safediv\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a \u000d\u000a (* Version 1.6.1\u000d\u000a  * Tested and corrected various bugs related to 1.6.0\u000d\u000a  *)\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a(* Version 1.6.2\u000d\u000a * Corrected bug with standalone feeding\u000d\u000a * Adding Baumer Encoder\u000d\u000a  * Made slight modifications to the way stroke press and auto cycle works in order to prevent having an option for an external safety controller.\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a \u000d\u000a (* Version 1.6.3\u000d\u000a  * Deleted ENO of SafeCAM - problem with UserIO\u000d\u000a  * Put Sharpening_Data in retained.\u000d\u000a  *)\u000d\u000a  \u000d\u000a  (* Version 1.6.4\u000d\u000a   * Corrected minor problems with contactors, overload woudln't stop the maintain contact.\u000d\u000a   * Corrected bug with the running icon when using contactors\u000d\u000a   * Made sure to prevent the press from restarting automatically if palms are maintained on the console and there is a someone in front of the curtains and then not anymore on the \u000d\u000a   * Schneider safety PLCs\u000d\u000a   * Added calc_misc to tasks\u000d\u000a   * Prevented contactors for adjustment motors from automatically restart when light curtains are let go of\u000d\u000a   * Standardized SFT signals \u000d\u000a   * Last version before servopress integration\u000d\u000a   *)\u000d\u000a   \u000d\u000a(* Version 2.0.0\u000d\u000a * Adding servopress\u000d\u000a * Added an air required option for presses that require it (conventional and high tonnage servo)\u000d\u000a * Added a new CAM that uses the continue mode\u000d\u000a * Set new default values for the press retained variables\u000d\u000a * Added messages to UIO\u000d\u000a * Tested the new program, made adjustments to :\u000d\u000a \u0009\u0009Automatic single stroke, pendulum, full, UIO\u000d\u000a *)\u000d\u000a \u000d\u000a (* Version 2.1.0\u000d\u000a  * Added tonnage monitoring from Assa Abloy, integration to be tested in the future.\u000d\u000a  *)\u000d\u000a  \u000d\u000a  (* Version 2.2.0\u000d\u000a   * Added ability to have 4 encoders on the straightner.\u000d\u000a   * Adding ability to have two HMIs\u000d\u000a   *)\u000d\u000a \u000d\u000a  (* Version 2.2.1\u000d\u000a   * Added ability to have linear encoders instead of cam absed ones for the straightner\u000d\u000a   * Tested most of the new features and corrected some minor bugs midway through Bluescope CTL\u000d\u000a   *)\u000d\u000a   \u000d\u000a   (* Version 2.2.2\u000d\u000a    * Minor bug fixes for some items on the HMI (taken from the new instruction manual tests)\u000d\u000a\u0009* Incorporated some bug fixes from BlueScope CTL\u000d\u000a\u0009* Added ability for uncoiler to use vector speed control\u000d\u000a\u0009*)\u000d\u000a   \u000d\u000a  (* Version 2.2.3\u000d\u000a   * Correcting minor bugs with Baumer encoder\u000d\u000a   * Need to figure out what is going on with Calibration rung 0 (line 39 & 40) (Press.Speed not working?) Check on Delstar\u000d\u000a   \u000d\u000aVersion_Number_String := '2.2.3';","W":1156}],"LRI":1,"RRI":2,"VLs":[]}
